\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n佢話呢度做野預左夜夜OT, 無時間比你拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b05bfa62d5c4d3a303ccfcecb8ffbd414313a4","tid":2217390,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b36a14231284868e52d7de749ee89871b9eb31d4","tid":2217390,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"俾人串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509120b46837b8994c235ccd024864341135f25c","tid":2217390,"uid":134103,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算係見工嘅趣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說有一年暑期工去咗in某大公司嘅sales，咁呢份工係講明請大專生做暑期工，所以成班都係差唔多年紀咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多廿個人上去interview，in完之後有個應該係team head嘅人走出嚟，話基本上大家都冇咩問題，不過返工之前要過三日training先，最ON9係training係冇錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要過咗training先決定請唔請，如果請嘅先會當你返training嘅日子係返工出返糧俾你，仲要講明淨係請兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾個聽完已經即刻走，其實我都想走，不過嗰時未搵到其他工，暑假又好得閒，就當係返去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁個training都冇咩特別，就係學下點sell客，如果遇到麻煩客要點做之類，其實好hea，不過好玩在可以識到其他同齡人，大家一齊玩，其中仲有一個女仔好靚女，差啲想主動識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來training完咗，個team head請咗嗰個好靚嘅女仔，理由唔使我解釋啦，做sales靚女梗係優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後另一個竟然係請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自問喺training嗰幾日都係鳩下鳩下，講嘢又柒下柒下咁，心諗有乜理由請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗正式簽約嗰刻，個team head問我：<br />\n<br />\n「Tenet仔，你知唔知點解我會請你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？」<br />\n<br />\n「Err&hellip; 唔知喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「因為我發覺你真係好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Training嗰幾日我一直留意你，發覺你真係好搞笑，為我哋帶來好多歡樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我想請你睇下你入到嚟我條tean會有咩表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n我聽完之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a780cce233c7232b2883623d7256e2560dd7f47","tid":2217390,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b36a14231284868e52d7de749ee89871b9eb31d4","tid":2217390,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"