Time":"2020-09-25T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"好彩我個樣生得夠幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔係都唔請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b719d5b1fdc302ce00ab54d6ca173385ccbf6d","tid":2217390,"uid":255069,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"0ca7c41f5bf51b04ccea641a8a677bb86a78be8c","tid":2217390,"uid":323000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e07748c8af672b4cc9372e4fef703a4d6250ae","tid":2217390,"uid":255069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"真人真事，十幾個人的group interview, 個interviewer 黑色薄衫真空突點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"男定女先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ce26523a4b68f58e3ac0f9d15d910ebe0b3055","tid":2217390,"uid":45232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"509120b46837b8994c235ccd024864341135f25c","tid":2217390,"uid":134103,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算係見工嘅趣事<i